{
  "stem": "11882.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But there was no discrimination whatsoever in promotions or-- which were more or less suspended for the duration of Nuremberg, anyway.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But the women were treated very well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There was no problem with that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Women lawyers-- there were not very many of them, but those that were there were given their cases to work on.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Sometimes they got a little disappointment, as he tells in his memoirs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Very capable women once or twice-- or a man, too-- was not allowed, after doing all the research on a trial, to go in and make the court presentation.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Great prestige, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because some man with more authority or pull, but it wasn't a question of sexual discrimination-- it was because that was a prize that someone felt would help them for their career in Washington later, or had a pull.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That's human.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Had an interest in that case.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then the man that had worked on it would be kind to sad.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Nobody had promised him-- or the woman-- that he was going to present it in court.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But women did present court cases, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They weren't always pulled out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "There was another reason than sex involved.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the really final days, I wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got a job a few weeks before the verdict came in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I left on the-- I know all these dates.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's a funny thing with my mind.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I left Nuremberg as an employee on 26th December, 1948, and went to Army intelligence.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I kept going back there and working also.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had a little leave left because there was work to be done-- wind-up work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was not much work for not many people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But there still were things that had to be polished up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And Dr.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
